{"tid":107770,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［好歌共賞］麥浚龍X周國賢︰True Romance","createTime":"2017-02-04T16:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T05:41:04.000Z","uid":67389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4e4f9bd25fb9b4a2d1068dcd5d922caff08df6","tid":107770,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">True Romance</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作曲：周國賢<br />\n作詞：周耀輝<br />\n編曲：恭碩良<br />\n監製：麥浚龍、于逸堯<br />\n<br />\n教我如何親近你<br />\n如樹上住的畫眉<br />\n曾路過甚麼小仙島<br />\n可有一剎飛過那些小青草<br />\n<br />\n教我如何思念你<br />\n如月亮做的好奇<br />\n能令我什麼都想知道<br />\n總有一剎看著我　或來自塵土<br />\n<br />\n＊你追的壯天空<br />\n　你捉的暖春風<br />\n　你心思多到　怎麼細訴<br />\n　這感覺多好　知道自己不知道<br />\n　但知是我　預知和你　會很好<br />\n<br />\n怪我明明不是你<br />\n如命運畫的距離<br />\n能令我什麼都想知道<br />\n總有一剎了解你　或來自晨早<br />\n<br />\nRepeat＊<br />\n<br />\n最好抬頭就有美麗一種<br />\n像泥地看畫眉<br />\n未明白已嫵媚<br />\n<br />\n你追的可撲空<br />\n你捉的可颳風<br />\n你心思多到　總有一剎閃過讓我剛剛看到<br />\n這感覺多好　知道自己不知道<br />\n便繼續想知道<br />\n繼續繼續虛得似天空<br />\n也真得似春風<br />\n也許更加滿足<br />\n為繼續繼續亦覺得好<br />\n時候亦有點早<br />\n你竟因我悠然飛到<br />\n怎愛你未必知道<br />\n誰是你或者想知道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBq_noIB_eY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnBq_noIB_eY&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ae5c9601\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBq_noIB_eY</a></div>"},{"pid":"e795bc486a8a997c6eb27fcc2d6851e243c01c6d","tid":107770,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"成隻天生地夢都好好聽，最鍾意就係呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c2ef7dac7bbfbf38e74765d6516cc9c93ce8b","tid":107770,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成隻天生地夢都好好聽，最鍾意就係呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma